{"tid":1010851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Ubisoft為《全境封鎖2》封測信件中「美國政府停擺」一說道歉","createTime":"2019-02-06T10:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T15:29:29.000Z","uid":88374,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"533d437d32117681b65f4ddeb55bfe1746bcb69c","tid":1010851,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:09:12.000Z","msg":"川普不大高興。<br />\n2019-02-03 00:37 By 歪力<br />\n<br />\n令人既期待又怕受傷害的《湯姆克蘭西：全境封鎖 2》（Tom Clancy&rsquo;s The Division 2）將在豬年大年初三的 2 月 7 日展開 Beta 封閉測試，畢竟關係到第一波玩家的反饋，Ubisoft 為此想必是嚴陣以待，只不過似乎在公關上出了一點小差錯，在海外引起不小關注。<br />\n<br />\n就在 2 月初，由 Ubisoft 寄給參與封測玩家的信件標題上，大剌剌的寫上「在 Beta 來看看真正的政府停擺會是什麼樣子」，令不少海外玩家紛紛在 Reddit 或是推特上引發話題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CiH4Rqd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCiH4Rqd.png&h=3cd96868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jS3S0iz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjS3S0iz.png&h=e5c1d585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著網路話題的延燒，Ubisoft 很快再度寄出信函，內文表示這是一項嚴重的程序錯誤，官方表示：「我們知道美國政府停擺的說詞會對數千人造成影響，我們不是故意要形成這樣的狀況。」並向玩家致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LZu2w8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LZu2w8.png&h=fd41d76f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，有鑑於美國總統川普上任後的國際政治局勢變化，在去年瑞典遊戲論壇（Sweden Game Conference），Ubisoft Massive 營運長 Alf Condelius 談話中便曾表示過他們希望遊戲能跟政府分開來看。不過，就算遊戲不想扯上政治，政治會找上他們，例如玻利維亞政府曾向法國 Ubisoft 提出抗議，理由就是《火線獵殺：野境》踩到了那條線。<br />\n<br />\nCondelius：不幸的是，如果你們想聽實話，這對做生意（商業上）也不大好... 不過有趣的是，這是我們目前還在思考的事，同時也是我們與玩家正在討論的議題。當然，因為人們對於我們所創造的世界總是會有自己的解讀，他們想在我們所建立的虛構世界裡找到屬於自己的真實感，對故事或遊戲來說都是如此。<br />\n<br />\n雖然這只是個公關失誤，但還是讓《全境封鎖 2》以另一種形式增添了話題。當然， Yves Guillemot 執行長自己也說過，Ubisoft 的遊戲確實是帶有政治面向的，只不過他們維持的是中立的政治立場。<br />\n<br />\n 《湯姆克蘭西：全境封鎖 2》（Tom Clancy&rsquo;s The Division 2）即將在 2019 年 3 月 15 日於 Epic Games Store 與 Uplay 上架。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/37943/ubisoft-apologizes-for-the-division-2-email-promising-a-real-government-shutdown\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F37943%2Fubisoft-apologizes-for-the-division-2-email-promising-a-real-government-shutdown&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTG0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=481284da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/37943/ubisoft-apologizes-for-the-division-2-email-promising-a-real-government-shutdown</a>"},{"pid":"c623f09fd410f02abe8ad9b6389d16945999139b","tid":1010851,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbb1422dbb74a19577265aa11b0adaa9a0a29a9","tid":1010851,"uid":89514,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:29:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e4d78ee555e00f6c37faba9306cd582a1065e22","tid":1010851,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:43:43.000Z","msg":"薯仔server"},{"pid":"4f921c01906210be9bb70eb54903451ef3b7748d","tid":1010851,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:45:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司學人串人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7787c34c20ae79f8699c63b04914b2e951a7c285","tid":1010851,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"講下笑又踩中班人g點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a968eab945bc2229bd15f2d4eb6c6839255852","tid":1010851,"uid":59832,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:18:20.000Z","msg":"Come see what a real server shutdown looks like in the Private Beta<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc34d75fd5a61a9b60d35c5ba594d6223634dbd","tid":1010